Class CoreProject

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.modelio.gproject.plugin.CoreProject

  • public class CoreProject
extends Object
    Represents the core.project plugin.

    Cannot respect the typical plugin singleton pattern because core plugins must not use osgi.
